---
export const prerender = true;
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { CONTACT_EMAIL } from '../data/links';
import '../styles/content-entry.css';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | Henrik Söderlund"
  description="Privacy policy for henriksoderlund.com - how personal information is collected, used, and protected."
>
  <div class="privacy-page">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

    <p class="dates">Last updated: 29 March 2026</p>

    <p>
      This privacy policy explains how personal information is collected, used, and protected when you visit
      henriksoderlund.com or use the contact form on this site. This site is operated by Henrik Söderlund,
      an independent technology consultant based in Perth, Australia.
    </p>

    <section class="content-entry">
      <h2 id="information-collected">Information Collected</h2>
      <p>
        This site collects personal information only when you voluntarily submit it through the contact form.
        The information collected includes your name, email address, and the content of your message.
      </p>
      <p>
        No account registration is required to browse this site. No cookies are set by this site directly.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="content-entry">
      <h2 id="how-information-is-used">How Your Information Is Used</h2>
      <p>
        Contact form submissions are used solely to respond to your enquiry. Your name and email address are
        included in the email sent to me so that I can reply to you directly. Form data is not stored in any
        database and is not used for marketing purposes.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="content-entry">
      <h2 id="third-party-services">Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>The following third-party services process data in connection with this site:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Cloudflare</strong> provides hosting, content delivery, and security services.
          Cloudflare processes standard web request data (IP addresses, browser information) as part of
          delivering pages and protecting against abuse.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Cloudflare Turnstile</strong> is used on the contact form to verify that submissions
          come from real visitors rather than automated bots. Turnstile sends your IP address and browser
          signals to Cloudflare for verification when the form is submitted.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Resend</strong> delivers the email generated by the contact form. Your name, email address,
          and message content are transmitted through Resend's email delivery infrastructure.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Google Tag Manager (server-side)</strong> is used for analytics via a server-side
          deployment on a first-party subdomain. Analytics data is processed server-side and does not
          set cookies in your browser.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Fou Analytics</strong> provides privacy-focused website analytics. Fou Analytics does not
          use cookies, does not collect personal information, and processes all data in compliance with
          GDPR and other privacy regulations.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="content-entry">
      <h2 id="external-links">External Links</h2>
      <p>
        This site contains links to external services including Calendly, LinkedIn, and GitHub. These are
        third-party websites with their own privacy policies. Clicking these links takes you outside of
        henriksoderlund.com, and this privacy policy does not apply to those sites.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="content-entry">
      <h2 id="data-retention">Data Retention</h2>
      <p>
        Contact form submissions are delivered as email and are not stored in any server-side database.
        Email correspondence is retained for the duration necessary to respond to your enquiry and manage
        any subsequent engagement.
      </p>
      <p>
        Analytics data collected by Fou Analytics and server-side GTM is aggregated and anonymised. No individual
        visitor profiles are created or retained.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="content-entry">
      <h2 id="your-rights">Your Rights</h2>
      <p>
        You may request access to, correction of, or deletion of any personal information held about you.
        To make a request, please contact me at
        <a href={`mailto:${CONTACT_EMAIL}`}>{CONTACT_EMAIL}</a>.
      </p>
      <p>
        This site is operated from Australia. If you are visiting from the European Union or United Kingdom,
        your data is processed in accordance with the same standards described in this policy. You have the
        right to lodge a complaint with your local data protection authority if you believe your personal
        information has been handled improperly.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="content-entry">
      <h2 id="changes">Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>
        This privacy policy may be updated from time to time. Any changes will be reflected on this page
        with an updated date. Continued use of the site after changes constitutes acceptance of the
        revised policy.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="content-entry">
      <h2 id="contact">Contact</h2>
      <p>
        If you have questions about this privacy policy or how your personal information is handled,
        please contact me at <a href="mailto:admin@henriksoderlund.com">admin@henriksoderlund.com</a>.
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
